28
00:01:52,888 --> 00:01:54,505
in dem, ⟨ot o⟩.

29
00:01:54,505 --> 00:01:55,481
un do,

30
00:01:55,555 --> 00:01:56,932
nisht ⟨get-⟩,

31
00:01:56,955 --> 00:02:00,276
a ayzerne hrubkele fle- iz geven,

32
00:02:00,276 --> 00:02:02,715
ober m'hot gehat mit vos tsu heytsn ⟨ober gornit⟩.

33
00:02:02,715 --> 00:02:06,204
in shtroy iz men gelign, eyns lebn s'andere, eyns lebn s'andere,

34
00:02:06,574 --> 00:02:07,912
in dem,

35
00:02:07,912 --> 00:02:09,131
kolkhoz.

36
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:17,681
ver iz dortn oyf di foto⟨grafye⟩?

37
00:02:16,243 --> 00:02:17,902
dos bin ikh,

38
00:02:17,902 --> 00:02:20,670
far der milkhome, nokh in der heym,

39
00:02:20,670 --> 00:02:24,844
a tsvey yor biz di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn, tsvey, dray yor,

40
00:02:25,153 --> 00:02:26,499
