46
00:02:45,437 --> 00:02:47,227
er hot mir geshikt es.

47
00:02:47,192 --> 00:02:48,193
a dank.

48
00:02:49,251 --> 00:02:50,568
un dos i-...

49
00:02:50,753 --> 00:02:53,749
ver iz ot do oyf yene fotograf⟨ye⟩?

50
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:55,134
ot do iz mayn muter.

51
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,249
dos iz mayn muter.

52
