59
00:03:19,644 --> 00:03:21,347
rikhtike mame.

60
00:03:21,853 --> 00:03:22,792
a dank.

61
00:03:40,753 --> 00:03:41,450
UNK

62
00:03:41,450 --> 00:03:42,182
⟨nu⟩?

63
