dos bin ikh teykef...

68
00:04:00,244 --> 00:04:02,720
yor zekhtsn bin ikh alt do.

69
00:04:03,062 --> 00:04:03,900
a dank.

70
00:04:07,264 --> 00:04:09,738
di, dos bild,

71
00:04:09,846 --> 00:04:13,652
