74
00:04:22,617 --> 00:04:27,661
hob ikh im geshikt mayn kleyn bild, un er hot mir krikgeshikt dos bild fun im.

75
00:04:27,661 --> 00:04:30,563
azoy az mayn foter iz er,

76
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:32,537
Gershn Bernshteyn.

77
00:04:32,946 --> 00:04:35,898
un er hot gemakht fun dem bild

78
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:36,505
fun dem kleynem bild

79
00:04:36,505 --> 00:04:38,542
ot dos groyse bild

80
00:04:36,535 --> 00:04:37,535
a ⟨bild⟩...?

81
00:04:38,685 --> 00:04:40,484
fun zikh mit mir.

82
00:04:41,301 --> 00:04:45,530
