114
00:06:28,778 --> 00:06:30,571
BARUKH dayen emes.

115
00:06:30,803 --> 00:06:31,584
⟨a⟩ dank.

116
00:06:31,596 --> 00:06:33,378
un ikh mit mayn man...

117
00:06:35,983 --> 00:06:38,744
dos bin ikh mit mayn man mit di kinder,

118
00:06:39,038 --> 00:06:41,023
ven zey zenen nokh geven kleyn.

119
00:06:41,333 --> 00:06:43,402
geven a sheyne mishpokhe

120
00:06:43,408 --> 00:06:45,743
un ales, nor a kurts lebn.

121
00:06:46,378 --> 00:06:48,346
er iz yung geshtorbn,

122
00:06:48,403 --> 00:06:50,504
